      "comment": "SUPER SPECIAL (1) has an excellent record over this journey having never missed the placings in five starts, including two wins and three placings. Placed last time (35.25) at this track in a Restricted WIN, finishing third and beaten 7 lengths. Looks well placed and should feature. JENNY DUTTON (3) jumped from this box and placed but in quick time latest (35.00) at this track over 600m in a Restricted WIN. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. JIMMY LEGS (6) spotted a start but wound up strongly late and finished second and beaten 1.75 lengths (20.14) at Capalaba in P5. Expected to be in the finish again. RITZA TOBY (7) is worth a look despite no experience at this trip.",
